HEADWORD: Continuer
<hw>Con*tin"u*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
continues; one who has the power of perseverance or persistence.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧Indulgent <xex>continuers</xex> in sin.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Hammond.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I would my horse had the speed of your tongue, and so good a
<qex>continuer</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Continuity</ent>⟦br⟧
